  "instructions": [
    "Heat a robata grill to 400\u00100F (200\u00100C).",
    "Brush the Romano pepper with olive oil and season with salt, black pepper, and Australian bush herb blend.",
    "Roast the pepper on the grill for 10 minutes per side, or until slightly charred and tender.",
    "Meanwhile, mix the candy and lemon juice in a small bowl.",
    "Once the pepper is cooked, slice it open lengthwise and fill with the candy mixture.",
    "Return the pepper to the grill for 2-3 minutes, or until the candy is caramelized and bubbly.",
    "Remove the pepper from the grill and serve with roasted garlic and Australian yogurt."
